Optimisation loss functions for each stage:

| Stage    | Main Metric     | Sensible Alternatives                       |
| -------- | --------------- | ------------------------------------------- |
| C1       | Win Rate        | Expectancy, Profit Factor, Net Return       |
| C2       | Win Rate        | Expectancy, Trade Duration, Trade Freq      |
| Baseline | Max Drawdown    | Sharpe, Ulcer Index, Streaks, Volatility    |
| Volume   | Profit Factor   | Return/Trade, % Time In, Missed Winners     |
| Exit     | Avg. R-Multiple | Avg Win/Loss, Median Hold, Equity Smoothing |
